testRun.title: NetBeans IDE 8.0 Full Testing - NetCAT
testRun.desc:
Full test of NetBeans IDE 8.0 development builds [1]. Ideally use latest build of JDK 8 [2]. All testers are required to finish their testing by Monday - February 17th 8:00 AM UTC [3].

[1] http://bits.netbeans.org/netbeans/trunk/nightly
[2] https://jdk8.java.net/download.html
[3] http://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?iso=20140217T0800
